channel.title: My server
channel.description:
My server brettownz.no-ip.biz
Please Read!!! my server is much better than most other servers, it is a 24/7 server and you have a better chance to become a mod or admin on my server, if you click on lets say a monster they have a code, like 233, with that code you can become that monster, all you have to do it type :npc 233, and to change back logout/ or type ::normal... but do do this you have to be a mod or admin and if you are a mod or admin type :ickup 00995 999999999 for max money... and all the codes on frugooscape and moparscape are the same on my server but you type lets say on frugooscape its 4151 1 on my server you type 04151 1 because you have more items on my server, if you become a admin you can type ::master for all 99 stats and if that doesnt work theres a back-up code :ure and it gives you all 99 stats and all skill capes and hoods... to get on my server type brettownz.no-ip.biz, on silab client.... =D have fun!!!
P.S. go on silab client to play!!!
